       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. AddTwoNumbers.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 NUM1          PIC 9(5) VALUE 1.
       01 NUM2          PIC 9(5) VALUE 2.
       01 RESULT        PIC 9(6) VALUE 3.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-PARAGRAPH1.
           DISPLAY "Enter the first number: " WITH NO ADVANCING.
           ACCEPT Num1.
           DISPLAY "Enter the second number: " WITH NO ADVANCING.
           ACCEPT NUM2.
           COMPUTE RESULT = NUM1 + NUM2.
           DISPLAY "The result of addition is: " RESULT.
           STOP RUN.
